#ot-pc-content>div>div.ot-sdk-four.ot-sdk-columns.ot-tab-list>ul>li:nth-child(5)>div {
    display: none;
}

#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-pc-header {
    display: table;
}

#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-title-cntr {
    padding: 10px;
    display: table-cell;
}

#onetrust-pc-sdk #ot-pc-title {
    text-overflow: initial;
    white-space: normal;
    word-wrap: break-word;
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 425px) and (max-width: 896px){
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-pc-logo {
    margin-left: 0px;
    margin-top: 5px;
    width: 75px;
}
#onetrust-consent-sdk #onetrust-pc-sdk h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: normal;
}
}

/* circle on */
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-tgl input:checked+.ot-switch .ot-switch-nob:before{
    background-color: #4285f4;
}

/* bar on */
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-tgl input:checked+.ot-switch .ot-switch-nob{
    background-color: #cddcf2;
}

/* bar off */
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-switch-nob{
    background-color: #f2f1f1;
}

/* circle off */
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-switch-nob:before{
    background-color: #7d7d7d;
}

/*Save button */
#onetrust-pc-sdk.ot-ftr-stacked .save-preference-btn-handler{
    min-width: 25%;
}

/*Logo */
@media(max-width: 767px){
    #onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-pc-logo{
        width: 50%;
    }
}

@media(max-width: 425px){
    #onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-pc-header .ot-pc-logo{
        width: 50%;
    }
}

#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-pc-logo.ot-pc-logo{
    height: 50px;
}
